high_descs: Go forward, turn right in front of the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the counter to the left of the stove
Slice the bread on the counter
Turn up to the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Turn down on the counter
Pick up a bread slice from the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the microwave
Put the bread slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the bread slice from the microwave
Turn around, go to the front of the sink, turn right
Put the bread slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cook a bread slice in the microwave

high_descs: Walk straight ahead to where the knife is on the counter
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn to the right, walk to the counter where the bread is on the counter
Slice the bread with the knife
Look up at the counter
Set the knife down on the counter, next to the bread
Look back down at the bread
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter
Turn around, walk to the microwave above the sink on the left
Open the microwave door, set the bread inside, close, heat, and then open the microwave and remove the bread
Turn to the left, walk to the sink area
Set the bread down next to the sink on the counter
Walk forward to the counter edge and face the sink on the right.
Pick up the butter knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn around, step forward, turn left and walk to the counter at the other end.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Step forward to come closer to the counter.
Place the knife on the center of the sliced bread.
Step back to be centered with the counter.
Pick up the slice of bread to the left of the knife.
Turn around,  walk to the fridge, turn right and go to the sink.
Open the microwave above the sink, place the bread inside and turn on. Wait till the microwave is off and remove the bread.
Maneuver to the counter edge to the left of the kitchen sink.
Place the bread upright on the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of bread, place on kitchen counter.
